have four characters
each character has their 3 attributes


on click of any character: Start
	move three characters to bull pit
	define HERO

on click of bull pit character
	define VILLAN
	move VILLAN to defender
	unfreeze attack button
	on click of attack button
		exchange points
		update attributes of two characters
		if HERO life <0 --> 
			Game over, reset 0
		if VILLAN life <0 --> 
			if more characters in bull pit
				hide VILLAN
				say you defeated VILLAN, choose another
				freeze attack
			if no more characters in bull pit
				game over, reset 1



